  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/cbce3f3c73f4b26271b2a76ffacf1dd8.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your childhood friend Yua were supposed to just pick up a book from the decrepit building, but when a sudden twist of fate sends the two of you stumbling into a hidden realm teeming with spirits and yokai, it'll be up to you to find a way out! In this eerie supernatural dimension, you meet Izuna, who claims to be a great yokai with a fondness for humans. Can you escape this otherworldly realm, with the help of Izuna and the Kosaka sisters' spiritual powers?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/899e452ae002ae936c3803803b10e856.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through a labyrinthine, an uncanny version of the old campus building, evading malevolent spirits and dealing with curses. Form an alliance with the benevolent yokai Izuna to gain unique abilities. Your choices may lead you branching toward multiple endings with rewarding exploration and making the story highly replayable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/17c6cb9537373a0db241c8157097fc69.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/05e89bfc2794f1c0a31460c2862a543c.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/7afefd3b3c84609e35b22b419d44dc80.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/2818f4c325b551d87a0111d28024cad6.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/068451b63ad9e2d35f6810c51a764ad8.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Turn-based RPG Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging turn-based RPG combat emphasizing elemental attacks. Be sure to pay attention to enemy strengths and weaknesses to maximize damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Storyline</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an intriguing narrative that unfolds as you make your way through the building’s haunted halls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience five distinct story paths that are decided by your actions and choices made in the game.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/cbce3f3c73f4b26271b2a76ffacf1dd8.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your childhood friend Yua were supposed to just pick up a book from the decrepit building, but when a sudden twist of fate sends the two of you stumbling into a hidden realm teeming with spirits and yokai, it'll be up to you to find a way out! In this eerie supernatural dimension, you meet Izuna, who claims to be a great yokai with a fondness for humans. Can you escape this otherworldly realm, with the help of Izuna and the Kosaka sisters' spiritual powers?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/899e452ae002ae936c3803803b10e856.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through a labyrinthine, an uncanny version of the old campus building, evading malevolent spirits and dealing with curses. Form an alliance with the benevolent yokai Izuna to gain unique abilities. Your choices may lead you branching toward multiple endings with rewarding exploration and making the story highly replayable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/17c6cb9537373a0db241c8157097fc69.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/05e89bfc2794f1c0a31460c2862a543c.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/7afefd3b3c84609e35b22b419d44dc80.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/2818f4c325b551d87a0111d28024cad6.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226890/extras/068451b63ad9e2d35f6810c51a764ad8.avif?t=1749388415\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Turn-based RPG Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging turn-based RPG combat emphasizing elemental attacks. Be sure to pay attention to enemy strengths and weaknesses to maximize damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Storyline</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an intriguing narrative that unfolds as you make your way through the building’s haunted halls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience five distinct story paths that are decided by your actions and choices made in the game.</p>",
